name: Cristina Arnold
text: I have eaten here many times.  I have always enjoyed the staff and food.  Best pizza around.

name: Helen Horne
text: Very good food. Love the people

name: Robert Gregory
text: Service is good food is good if they make a mistake or if they don't cook your food right if it's cooked too hard or anyting they will replace it with another one free of charge the next time you come in get it for For take out if you are dining in they will replace it right then... They will make you happy one way or the other...

name: Todd Hendrix
text: Thankfully this location has permanently closed.

text: Cool staff, pizza was on made well.

name: Richard Smith
text: Very dirty. Poor health score. Long wait times. And the General Manager is very rude and unprofessional towards her employees and customers. I am amazed that this restaurant is still in business.

text: Pizza wasn't as good as it usually is . the service was good.

text: The pizza is good, the delivery drivers are very nice but the general manager is very rude. She doesn't take care of her employees or customers.

text: I went in and it's a cold day, it was cold outside and inside, I ask could they turn the heat up, they said "it's on", I'm shivering, I ask again "r u sure it's on, can u turn it up"? Her reply, "no the cooks will get hot."
